title: Tawa -The King of the Jungle (1950) Adventure film - directed by Robert Emmett

sources.title: Tawa -The King of the Jungle (1950) Adventure film - directed by Robert Emmett
sources.description:
Hunter Tom Burton takes a cash mission to extract jungle boy Tawa from the wild, but Tamba the chimp and a grumpy gorilla crash his paycheck party. When Tawa's animal family fights back, Tom must choose: deliver the 'wild child' or let nature keep its own.

Original tittle: Forbidden Jungle (1950)
Directed by Robert Emmett Tansey

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/-VHKVkzMDpo

MAIN CAST
Don C. Harvey ➞ Tom Burton (The Hunter)
Forrest Taylor ➞ Trader Kirk
Alyce Louis ➞ Nita
Robert Cabal ➞ Tawa (The Jungle Boy)
Tamba the Chimp ➞ Herself
Ray Corrigan ➞ Gege the Gorilla
